    "body": "> Any ideas? Should I try to rebuild the DB?\r\n\r\nYes. You should resync using checkpoint sync and the `--purge-db` flag (or delete the database directory manually).\r\n\r\nhttps://lighthouse-book.sigmaprime.io/checkpoint-sync.html\r\n\r\nSometimes power outages can cause this sort of corruption. There's not much we can do about it in Lighthouse as this is mostly a property of LevelDB.",
